                                <td align="left" style="font-size: 8pt; color: Gray; padding: 6px;">
                                    By signing up, I agree to the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy and agree to receive
                                    additional survey, market research and other relevant offers from Surveys4Moms.com
                                </td>
                            </tr>*@
